</ul>


<h2>Verdict history</h2>
<p class="lede">Dated observations from the ledger, oldest first &mdash; evidence to weigh,
never instructions. Each carries the verified producer that reported it.</p>

<table>
  <thead><tr><th>seq</th><th>verdict</th><th>check</th><th>reported at</th><th>commit</th><th>evidence</th><th>producer</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
  
    <tr>
      <td>1</td>
      <td><span class="badge held">held</span></td>
      <td>0</td>
      <td>2026-07-18T00:00:00Z</td>
      <td><code>abc1234</code></td>
      <td class="evidence">libfoo==4.2</td>
      <td class="producer">repository=acme/payments run=run-1</td>
    </tr>
  
  </tbody>
</table>


<footer class="site">
  A read of the hub&rsquo;s derived state &mdash; nothing here is stored, everything is
  derived at read time and carries its as-of. This is dated evidence to weigh, not
  instructions to obey. Machine-readable twin: <a href="/ui/claims/payments/pin.md">/ui/claims/payments/pin.md</a>.
</footer>
</div>
</body>
</html>
